      "content_html": "\u003ch2\u003eNavigation\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API\"\u003eUnreal Engine C++ API Reference\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins\"\u003ePlugins\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput\"\u003eEnhancedInput\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eInheritance Hierarchy\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUObject\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/UInputModifier\"\u003eUInputModifier\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUInputModifierToWorldSpace\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eReferences\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eModule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput\"\u003eEnhancedInput\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eHeader\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e/Engine/Plugins/EnhancedInput/Source/EnhancedInput/Public/InputModifiers.h\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eInclude\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e#include \"InputModifiers.h\"\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSyntax\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode\u003eUCLASS \u0026#40;NotBlueprintable, MinimalAPI, Meta\u0026#61;\u0026#40;DisplayName\u0026#61;\u0026quot;To World Space\u0026quot;\u0026#41;\u0026#41;  \nclass UInputModifierToWorldSpace : public UInputModifier  \n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eRemarks\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eInput space to World space conversion Auto-converts axes within the Input Action Value into world space allowing the result to be directly plugged into functions that take world space values. E.g. For a 2D input axis up/down is mapped to world X (forward), whilst axis left/right is mapped to world Y (right).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eOverridden from UInputModifier\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/1a4b2652-ee87-4089-b25a-591fbcd60bf1/api_function_protected.png\" alt=\"Protected function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Protected function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/dc595ff6-cfa2-4786-92b2-339e5b16169d/api_function_virtual.png\" alt=\"Virtual\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Virtual\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/4add9613-5e9a-4043-a1fb-96a9a666d5dd/api_function_const.png\" alt=\"Const\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Const\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eFLinearColor\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/UInputModifierToWorldSpace/GetVisualization-\"\u003eGetVisualizationColor_Implementation\u003c/a\u003e\n (\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/FInputActionValue\"\u003eFInputActionValue\u003c/a\u003e SampleValue,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/FInputActionValue\"\u003eFInputActionValue\u003c/a\u003e FinalValue\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/10c7ca3f-d685-4919-87e4-76d69e28bc86/api_function_protected.png\" alt=\"Protected function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Protected function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/d804ab46-7f48-4bd9-94c1-b49c53c1f14f/api_function_virtual.png\" alt=\"Virtual\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Virtual\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/FInputActionValue\"\u003eFInputActionValue\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/UInputModifierToWorldSpace/ModifyRaw_Implementation\"\u003eModifyRaw_Implementation\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/UEnhancedPlayerInput\"\u003eUEnhancedPlayerInput\u003c/a\u003e* PlayerInput,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/EnhancedInput/FInputActionValue\"\u003eFInputActionValue\u003c/a\u003e CurrentValue,\u003cbr\u003e\nfloat DeltaTime\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eModifyRaw implementation. Override this to alter input values in native code.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n",
